Package entity

Class ReplenishmentRequest

Object
ReplenishmentRequest
public class ReplenishmentRequest extends Object
Represents a request for replenishment of a specific medicine, including details about the requested quantity, the pharmacist who requested it, and its processing status.

      Constructs a new replenishment request with the specified medicine, requested quantity, pharmacist, and request date/time. The status is initially set to PENDING.
      Parameters:
      medicine - The medicine being requested for replenishment.
      requestedQuantity - The quantity of the medicine being requested.
      requestedBy - The pharmacist who requested the replenishment.
      requestDateTime - The date and time when the replenishment request was made.
